Once the user is created in the system then it will be notified by the following measures 

1. SMS
2. Email

In SMS -> the user will be notified withe template like notification with the subject and the body of the message for the successulll login, or simply by the notification of the
          sms 

In Email the user will be notified in the email of it's login id in the device.

In SP users creation the admin have the major role to play it will create the final approval for the user confirmation.

Roles are assigned to the user according to it's criteria which it has been assigned.
